Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:10.77,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从不打算成为丧家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:13.97,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K69}汗{\K37}は{\K29}ス{\K44}パ{\K25}イ{\K50}ス
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:13.97,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗水是调味料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:16.73,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K57}傷{\K55}跡{\K106}輝{\K47}く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:16.73,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤痕在闪耀
